has been amazing. So amazing, that the amount of players hitting
the game overwhelmed our servers within a matter of minutes.

As a big thank you to our patient players throughout the event,
every player will receive 5,000 gold and 3 Core Set 2019 packs by
Wednesday, July 25.

The special events are gone for now, but we hope you continue to
play and enjoy the game. Our servers are now mostly stable and
scaled for a bunch more players, but there are a lot of you still
in there. We may still see service issues 
